sentences.en: Melt the butter over a medium-low heat. When it is melted and bubbly, put in the flour.
sentences.cn: 用中低火把黄油加热。待黄油熔化起泡后，放入面粉。

sentences.en: From the "Reset to" list, select Medium-low.
sentences.cn: 从“Reset to”列表中，选择Medium - low。

sentences.en: Change the security level for the Trusted sites from the default Medium to medium-low.
sentences.cn: 将Trusted sites的安全级别从默认值Medium更改为Medium - Low。
